<div class="content-wrapper">
  <h2>📚 About <%= siteData.siteName %></h2>

  <div class="card" style="margin-bottom: 2rem;">
    <p style="font-size: 1.05rem; line-height: 1.8;">
      <strong>VocationConnect</strong> is a modern professional development platform designed to bridge the gap between current students and experienced alumni. Our mission is to facilitate meaningful mentorship, career guidance, and interview preparation through authentic professional connections.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="grid" style="margin-bottom: 2rem;">
    <div class="card">
      <div style="font-size: 2rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;">🎯</div>
      <h3 style="margin-top: 0;">Our Mission</h3>
      <p>Empower students with real-world career insights and interview practice opportunities through meaningful connections with experienced alumni professionals.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
      <div style="font-size: 2rem; margin-bottom: 1rem;">🌟</div>
      <h3 style="margin-top: 0;">Why VocationConnect?</h3>
      <p>Unlike generic practice platforms, we connect you with real professionals who understand your field, your university, and your career aspirations.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <h3>✨ Key Features</h3>
  <ul class="features-list">
    <li><strong>Alumni Network:</strong> Access a diverse network of alumni across various industries and companies</li>
    <li><strong>Mock Interview Platform:</strong> Conduct realistic interview simulations with video, chat, and real-time feedback</li>
    <li><strong>Mentorship Opportunities:</strong> Build lasting professional connections with alumni mentors</li>
    <li><strong>Career Guidance:</strong> Get personalized advice on career paths, job searching, and professional development</li>
  </ul>

  <h3>👥 Who Benefits?</h3>
  <div class="grid">
    <div class="card">
      <div style="font-size: 1.75rem; margin-bottom: 0.75rem;">🎓</div>
      <h4>For Students</h4>
      <p>Gain confidence in your interview skills, learn about different career paths, and receive personalized guidance from professionals who've been in your shoes.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
      <div style="font-size: 1.75rem; margin-bottom: 0.75rem;">🤝</div>
      <h4>For Alumni</h4>
      <p>Give back to your alma mater, help shape the next generation of professionals, and stay meaningfully connected with your university community.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <h3>💻 Technology Stack</h3>
  <div class="card">
    <ul class="features-list" style="margin-top: 0;">
      <li><strong>Backend:</strong> Node.js with Express framework for fast, scalable APIs</li>
      <li><strong>Database:</strong> MySQL for robust, reliable data management</li>
      <li><strong>Templating:</strong> EJS for dynamic, responsive content rendering</li>
      <li><strong>Security:</strong> bcrypt password hashing and session-based authentication</li>
      <li><strong>Real-time Features:</strong> WebRTC for high-quality video communication</li>
    </ul>
  </div>
</div>
